title: Cafe Eclectic - Midtown
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Laid back cafe that offers a few vegan items and will make other dishes vegan upon request. At weekend brunch you could substitute tofu for scrambled eggs and veggie sausage for other meats. Has Wi-Fi, another location in Harbortown Square, Memphis.
